management

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • management.Course

  • public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
    The Course class stores attributes of a single course, that belongs to a CourseEntry.

    It contains a few constructors for the necessary initializations of attributes.

    Author:
    David
    See Also:
    Module, Entry, CourseEntry
